HE'S THE ONE WHO MAKES US WORK.

04:44.719 --> 04:45.981
-I DON'T KNOW.

04:46.111 --> 04:47.896
-DOES HE EVER TALK ABOUT ME?

04:48.026 --> 04:50.768
-OH, ME AND TODD, WE
SHOOT HOOP ONCE IN A WHILE.

04:50.899 --> 04:53.075
YOU KNOW, SAY HI IN THE HALL.

04:53.205 --> 04:54.903
BUT ME AND TODD, WE DON'T HANG.

04:55.033 --> 04:56.470
-YOU LIVE WITH HIM!

04:56.600 --> 04:59.821
-KIRSTIE, MY MOM IS
HIS PARENTS' MAID.

04:59.951 --> 05:03.390
I MEAN, WE LIVE IN THE BABY
BEAR GUESTHOUSE IN THE BACK.

05:03.520 --> 05:05.522
HE LIVES IN
THE BIG DADDY BEAR HOUSE.

05:05.653 --> 05:08.133
[CAR HORN HONKS]
[FUNKY ELECTRIC MUSIC]

05:09.178 --> 05:10.310
-HEY, THERE'S MR. WONDERFUL.

05:10.440 --> 05:11.876
GO. WHAT ARE YOU DOIN'?

05:12.007 --> 05:14.357
[KIRSTIE LAUGHS]

05:14.488 --> 05:17.142
[FUNKY ELECTRIC MUSIC]

05:29.154 --> 05:32.419
[MONITOR BEEPING RAPIDLY]

05:32.549 --> 05:36.205
-C.J., I'M TRYING TO
SLOW DOWN MY HEART RATE.

05:36.336 --> 05:38.425
-[CHUCKLES] OH, SORRY.

05:40.905 --> 05:43.865
IT'S GONNA BE THE LONGEST
FOUR MINUTES OF MY LIFE.

05:43.995 --> 05:45.867
-MINE, TOO.

05:45.997 --> 05:48.130
[MONITOR BEEPING SLOWS]

05:48.260 --> 05:49.523
-IS THE SLED READY, YET?

05:49.653 --> 05:51.263
-IT'S READY WHEN HE IS.

05:51.394 --> 05:52.352
-OKAY, HE'S JUST MEDITATING.

05:52.482 --> 05:53.483
HE SHOULD BE READY IN A MINUTE.

05:55.572 --> 05:58.532
[MONITOR BEEPING]

06:01.839 --> 06:03.493
HE'S DOWN TO 20 BEATS A MINUTE.

06:03.624 --> 06:06.235
[CODY EXHALES]

06:14.286 --> 06:15.897
FOUR MINUTES, MAX.

06:19.640 --> 06:22.120
[MONITOR BEEPING SLOWLY]

06:22.251 --> 06:23.165
-YOU READY?

06:25.776 --> 06:29.867
[MONITOR BEEPING SLOWLY]

06:34.089 --> 06:38.093
[APPREHENSIVE MUSIC]

06:49.974 --> 06:52.020
[METAL CLANGS]

06:56.764 --> 07:01.725
[ELECTRIFIED GUITAR RIFF]

07:14.956 --> 07:16.697
-ONE MINUTE.

07:16.827 --> 07:19.134
-HIS HEART RATE'S
DROPPED TO 18.

07:19.264 --> 07:24.356
[ELECTRIFIED GUITAR RIFF]

07:33.844 --> 07:35.106
-TWO MINUTES.

07:35.237 --> 07:36.717
-HE SHOULD BE REACHING
THE MARKER NOW.

07:39.154 --> 07:42.070
[MONITOR BEEPS]

07:42.200 --> 07:45.682
[ELECTRIFIED GUITAR RIFF]

07:57.694 --> 08:01.263
[LIGHT ORCHESTRAL MUSIC]

08:03.526 --> 08:05.876
-I COUNT 14 BEATS.
HE'S IN HIS ZONE.

08:07.965 --> 08:10.490
[LOUD WAILING]

08:15.843 --> 08:17.322
-CHRISTOPHER.

08:21.501 --> 08:23.938
[MONITOR BEEPING]
-HIS HEART RATE JUST JUMPED.

08:25.026 --> 08:26.201
-THREE MINUTES.

08:28.508 --> 08:31.032
[MYSTICAL PIANO MUSIC]

08:31.162 --> 08:35.166
[WATER BUBBLING]

08:37.604 --> 08:40.520
-COME ON, CODY,
INFLATE THE BALLOON.

08:44.261 --> 08:47.309
[ELECTRIFIED GUITAR RIFF]

08:56.753 --> 08:58.581
-HIS HEART RATE'S
ALL OVER THE PLACE!

08:58.712 --> 09:00.278
[MONITOR BEEPING RAPIDLY]

09:08.591 --> 09:09.766
[GASPING]

09:16.643 --> 09:17.687
-CODY, ARE YOU OKAY?

09:17.818 --> 09:18.993
-DO YOU WANT SOME OXYGEN?

09:19.123 --> 09:20.734
-OH, IT'S OKAY.

09:20.864 --> 09:22.170
-C.J.: YOU SCARED UP HALF
TO DEATH. WHAT HAPPENED?

09:22.300 --> 09:25.521
-I UH, I HEARD
SOMETHING. [PANTING]

09:25.652 --> 09:26.696
SAW SOMETHING.

09:28.263 --> 09:29.438
-WHAT DID YOU SEE?

09:30.221 --> 09:32.310
-I DON'T KNOW. [PANTING]

09:33.442 --> 09:35.009
I DON'T KNOW.

09:39.100 --> 09:40.928
[GASPING]

09:41.755 --> 09:43.278
[MAN TALKING INDISTINCTLY
IN BACKGROUND]

09:43.408 --> 09:45.541
[GIGGLING]

09:50.546 --> 09:51.416
[CAR HORN HONKS]

09:54.028 --> 09:56.596
[CAR ENGINE RUMBLES]

10:01.601 --> 10:03.428
-I TOLD YOU TO STAY
AWAY FROM HIM, KIRSTIE.

10:03.559 --> 10:04.865
-MRS. MORGAN,
I WANT YOU TO KNOW

10:04.995 --> 10:06.040
THAT I REALLY LIKE
YOUR DAUGHTER.

10:06.170 --> 10:07.519
-I HEAR YOU LIKE
A LOT OF GIRLS.

10:07.650 --> 10:09.173
-MOM!

10:09.304 --> 10:10.958
-I CHECKED, KIRSTIE.
DON'T THINK FOR ONE SECOND

10:11.088 --> 10:12.786
THAT YOU'RE THE ONLY GIRL
HE'S HAD IN THAT CAR,

10:12.916 --> 10:14.788
OR TAKEN OUT IN HIS
RICH DADDY'S BOAT.

10:14.918 --> 10:16.224
-STOP IT!

10:16.354 --> 10:17.704
-MRS. MORGAN, YOU
GOT IT ALL WRONG.

10:17.834 --> 10:19.923
IT'S DIFFERENT WITH
KIRSTIE. I LOVE HER.

10:20.054 --> 10:23.013
-YOU TWO ARE TOO YOUNG TO
EVEN KNOW WHAT LOVE IS ABOUT.

10:23.144 --> 10:23.927
NOW, LEAVE HER ALONE!

10:24.058 --> 10:25.233
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

10:25.363 --> 10:26.626
-I'M DOING
WHAT'S BEST FOR YOU.

10:26.756 --> 10:27.365
-HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHAT'S BEST FOR ME?

10:27.496 --> 10:29.106
-'CAUSE I KNOW.

10:29.237 --> 10:30.281
-KIRSTIE, KIRSTIE, IT'S OKAY.
-MRS. MORGAN: LET'S GO.

10:30.412 --> 10:31.456
-I'LL GO.
-KIRSTIE: NO.

10:31.587 --> 10:32.588
-INSIDE.
-TODD: WE'LL TALK LATER.

10:32.719 --> 10:33.328
-TODD!
-MRS. MORGAN: INSIDE!

10:38.333 --> 10:41.902
[CAR ENGINE RUMBLES]

10:43.251 --> 10:44.600
-HOW COULD YOU DO THAT TO ME?

10:45.819 --> 10:47.255
-BECAUSE I'M YOUR MOTHER

10:47.385 --> 10:48.691
AND I WON'T LET YOU RUIN
YOUR LIFE OVER A BOY.

10:48.822 --> 10:50.867
-RUIN? IT'S NORMAL
TO HAVE A BOYFRIEND!

10:50.998 --> 10:53.696
-WHAT'S NORMAL IS FOR
YOU TO GO TO SCHOOL.

10:53.827 --> 10:56.133
I WANT YOU TO BECOME
SOMEONE SPECIAL.

10:56.264 --> 10:58.832
I DON'T WANT YOU TO END UP
SERVING MEATLOAF AND COFFEE

10:58.962 --> 11:00.311
IN SOME GREASY DINER!

11:01.225 --> 11:03.184
-TODD IS SWEET.

11:04.489 --> 11:05.969
HE MAKES ME FEEL HAPPY.

11:06.100 --> 11:07.536
HE MAKES ME FEEL GOOD.

11:07.667 --> 11:09.320
-I WON'T LET YOU BECOME
ONE OF THOSE GIRLS

11:09.451 --> 11:10.974
WHO GETS PREGNANT AT 15,

11:11.105 --> 11:13.847
AND GETS MARRIED AT 16
IF THE BOY DOESN'T RUN AWAY

11:13.977 --> 11:15.979
AND LEAVE YOU ALONE TO
RAISE THE BABY BY YOURSELF.

11:17.067 --> 11:18.503
-IT'S NOT FAIR THAT
YOU KEEP BLAMING ME

11:18.634 --> 11:19.896
FOR WHAT HAPPENED TO YOU!

11:20.027 --> 11:22.420
THIS IS NOT YOUR
LIFE, IT'S MINE!

11:23.508 --> 11:24.640
[DOOR SLAMS]

11:30.298 --> 11:31.952
-A MERMAID?

11:32.082 --> 11:33.736
-NEWMIE: THERE'S NO SUCH
THING AS A MERMAID, CODY.

11:33.867 --> 11:36.260
-I KNOW, I KNOW.
I MUST BE GOIN' NUTS.

11:36.391 --> 11:37.914
-C.J.: I BELIEVE IN MERMAIDS.

11:38.045 --> 11:39.829
-YEAH, RIGHT, IN FOLKLORE,
LEGENDS OF THE SEA.

11:39.960 --> 11:41.309
-NO, IN REAL LIFE,
IN THE OCEAN.

11:41.439 --> 11:43.398
-C.J., HALF FISH,
HALF WOMAN, PLEASE!

11:44.181 --> 11:46.270
-C.J.: YOU SAID YOU HEARD
A WOMAN'S VOICE, RIGHT?

11:47.228 --> 11:49.230
-YEAH, BUT IT'S PROBABLY
JUST A GRAY WHALE SINGING.

11:49.360 --> 11:51.362
-COULD BE. SOUND TRAVELS
A LONG WAY UNDER WATER.

11:51.493 --> 11:53.538
-YEAH, A WHALE
SINGS CHRISTOPHER?

11:53.669 --> 11:54.888
THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID, RIGHT?

11:55.018 --> 11:56.541
-THAT'S WHAT I THOUGHT, BUT--

11:56.672 --> 11:58.282
-NEWMIE: IT'S
OXYGEN DEPRIVATION.

11:58.413 --> 12:00.415
-YOUR MIND'S PROBABLY JUST
GOING NUTS AT THAT DEPTH.

12:00.545 --> 12:02.852
-WELL, HIS HEART RATE WENT UP.
HE DEFINITELY SAW SOMETHING.

12:02.983 --> 12:04.506
-MAYBE IT WAS A SEA LION.

12:04.636 --> 12:07.030
-NO, IT WAS A DOLPHIN.
YOU PROBABLY SAW A DOLPHIN.

12:07.161 --> 12:10.381
-YEAH, WITH LONG BLONDE HAIR.
CODY, YOU SAW A MERMAID.

12:10.512 --> 12:14.124
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

12:14.255 --> 12:16.257
-WOMAN: SAMANTHA GILBERT
AND HER PARENTS ARE AT THE CLUB

12:16.387 --> 12:17.954
FOR DINNER TONIGHT.

12:18.085 --> 12:21.001
NOW THERE'S A YOUNG GIRL
YOU SHOULD ASK OUT, TODDY.

12:21.523 --> 12:24.091
-I ALREADY HAVE
A GIRLFRIEND, MOM.

12:24.221 --> 12:26.093
-[CHUCKLES] YOU DON'T
MEAN THAT YOUNG GIRL

12:26.223 --> 12:28.356
WHO LIVES IN THAT
TRAILER PARK, DO YOU?

12:28.486 --> 12:29.879
-HER NAME IS KIRSTIE.

12:30.010 --> 12:32.360
AND YES, YOU KNOW THAT'S
EXACTLY WHO I MEAN.

12:33.796 --> 12:36.451
-THIS KIRSTIE IS A LITTLE
YOUNGER THAN YOU, ISN'T SHE?

12:37.191 --> 12:38.670
-A YEAR.

12:39.454 --> 12:41.891
MOM'S YOUNGER THAN YOU.

12:42.587 --> 12:44.111
ANYWAY, DON'T WORRY.

12:44.241 --> 12:45.025
IT'S NOT LIKE WE'RE
GETTIN' MARRIED JUST YET.

12:45.155 --> 12:47.070
-NO, I UNDERSTAND.

12:47.201 --> 12:48.811
ANYWAY, COLLEGE IS
NOT TOO FAR OFF.

12:49.420 --> 12:51.509
-LET'S DON'T TALK ABOUT
DARTMOUTH AGAIN, OKAY, DAD?

12:51.640 --> 12:52.989
I TOLD YOU, I DON'T
WANNA GO THERE.

12:53.120 --> 12:54.730
-AND I TOLD YOU I PULLED
SOME VERY HEAVY STRINGS

12:54.861 --> 12:56.210
TO GET YOU IN.

12:56.340 --> 12:57.602
YOUR GRANDDAD WENT
THERE, I WENT THERE,

12:57.733 --> 12:59.126
AND YOU'RE GOING THERE.

12:59.256 --> 13:00.823
-I DON'T CARE IF I'M
SOME STUPID LEGACY.

13:00.954 --> 13:02.346
I ALREADY SAID
I DON'T WANNA GO.

13:03.739 --> 13:05.959
KIRSTIE AND I ARE
THINKIN' ABOUT SANTA CRUZ.

13:06.568 --> 13:08.396
SOMETHING SMALL AND
CLOSE TO THE WATER.

13:08.526 --> 13:09.876
-END OF DISCUSSION, TODDY.

13:10.006 --> 13:11.878
NO GIRL WHO LIVES
IN A RUSTY OLD TRAILER

13:12.008 --> 13:13.967
IS KEEPING YOU
AWAY FROM A CAREER.

13:16.186 --> 13:19.537
-IT'S ABOUT MONEY,
AGAIN. IT ALWAYS IS.

13:21.104 --> 13:23.063
KIRSTIE AND HER MOM
DON'T HAVE MUCH MONEY,

13:23.193 --> 13:24.542
BUT DON'T WORRY.

13:24.673 --> 13:26.066
THEY'RE NOT GONNA
TRY AND STEAL OURS.

13:26.196 --> 13:27.328
-DON'T TALK THAT WAY
TO YOUR MOTHER, TODD.

13:29.112 --> 13:29.896
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

13:30.026 --> 13:31.680
-OUT OF HERE.

13:31.811 --> 13:33.769
-YOU STAY AWAY FROM THAT
GIRL, TODD. DO YOU HEAR ME?

13:33.900 --> 13:35.118
TODD!

13:36.816 --> 13:39.731
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

13:46.216 --> 13:49.872
[WAVES CRASHING]

13:51.004 --> 13:53.833
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

14:01.753 --> 14:03.320
-I HATE IT.

14:03.451 --> 14:05.845
THEY THINK THEY OWN ME,
LIKE A PET DOG OR SOMETHIN'.

14:05.975 --> 14:08.021
"DON'T DO THAT, TODD."
"TRY THIS, TODD."

14:08.151 --> 14:10.153
"WHY DON'T YOU TAKE
HER OUT, TODDY?"

14:12.242 --> 14:13.374
-WHO?

14:13.504 --> 14:15.332
-SAMANTHA GILBERT.

14:16.594 --> 14:17.726
-OH.

14:19.206 --> 14:21.251
I KNOW WHO SHE IS.
SHE'S A CHEERLEADER.

14:22.992 --> 14:24.385
AND SHE'S PRETTY.

14:26.996 --> 14:29.172
-HER FOLKS ARE RICH
IS WHAT IT'S ALL ABOUT.

14:33.437 --> 14:34.830
-DO YOU WANT TO?

14:35.352 --> 14:36.658
-WHAT?

14:37.833 --> 14:39.226
-GO OUT WITH HER?

14:40.444 --> 14:41.706
-NO.

14:43.360 --> 14:45.710
NO, I'M JUST TIRED OF
PEOPLE TELLIN' ME WHAT TO DO

14:45.841 --> 14:47.103
AND HOW TO LIVE MY LIFE.

14:51.499 --> 14:52.848
-WHAT DO YOU WANNA DO?

14:54.545 --> 14:55.938
-I WANNA BE WITH YOU.

14:58.027 --> 15:02.205
I WANT US TO BE
TOGETHER. FOREVER.

15:03.076 --> 15:03.903
YOU?

15:06.557 --> 15:10.474
-[GASPS] I NEVER
WANNA LOSE YOU.

15:12.694 --> 15:14.565
I'D BE SO AFRAID WITHOUT YOU.

15:19.962 --> 15:23.052
-WE'LL BE TOGETHER.
FOREVER, OKAY?

15:24.662 --> 15:26.403
NO MATTER WHAT IT TAKES.

15:27.013 --> 15:28.492
-NO MATTER WHAT.

15:29.537 --> 15:32.932
[LIGHT PIANO MUSIC]

15:41.941 --> 15:44.769
[SLOW DRUM BEAT]

15:46.902 --> 15:50.427
