17:45.629 --> 17:46.761
-MELLISANDE.

17:49.155 --> 17:50.808
MELLISANDE.

17:52.462 --> 17:53.898
MELLISANDE.

17:56.510 --> 17:57.554
[CODY GROANS]

17:57.685 --> 17:59.774
-MELLISANDE?
-CODY: WHAT?

17:59.904 --> 18:02.037
-MELLISANDE, THAT'S WHAT
YOU WERE SAYING. WHO IS SHE?

18:02.168 --> 18:03.821
[CODY GROANS]

18:03.952 --> 18:05.258
-I MUST HAVE BEEN DREAMING.

18:05.388 --> 18:07.347
-ABOUT ANOTHER WOMAN?

18:07.477 --> 18:10.828
-NO. I WAS DREAMING
ABOUT THE MERMAID.

18:12.482 --> 18:16.007
-OH, MELLISANDE.
THAT MUST BE HER NAME.

18:16.138 --> 18:18.009
-IT WAS A DREAM, C.J.

18:18.140 --> 18:21.883
-MAYBE, MAYBE NOT.

18:22.013 --> 18:24.755
MERMAIDS ARE VERY TELEPATHIC.
THAT'S HOW THEY COMMUNICATE.

18:24.886 --> 18:26.975
I JUST READ THAT RIGHT HERE.

18:28.933 --> 18:32.023
-THIS BOOK IS FICTION, BABY.
IT'S FANTASY, HONEY.

18:35.592 --> 18:36.376
-IS SHE PRETTY?

18:36.506 --> 18:39.118
-[CHUCKLES] WHY?

18:39.248 --> 18:40.554
ARE YOU JEALOUS?

18:40.684 --> 18:41.816
-NO.

18:43.296 --> 18:44.645
[SIGHS] IS SHE BLONDE?

18:44.775 --> 18:46.647
-LOOK, C.J.,
IT WAS A DREAM.

18:46.777 --> 18:48.605
LAST TIME IT WAS
OXYGEN DEPRIVATION.

18:48.736 --> 18:51.521
THERE ARE NO SUCH THING
AS MERMAIDS, OKAY?

18:54.045 --> 18:57.136
-OKAY, IF THAT'S WHAT YOU SAY.

19:00.226 --> 19:01.096
RED HEAD?

19:02.010 --> 19:02.880
[CHUCKLES]

19:08.799 --> 19:11.498
-MANNY: ALL RIGHT,
TODD. WAY TO GO, KIRSTIE.

19:13.587 --> 19:15.980
YES! ALL RIGHT. YOU
GUYS WERE AWESOME.

19:16.111 --> 19:17.373
-KIRSTIE!

19:18.722 --> 19:20.637
LET'S GO.
I'VE GOT A SPLIT SHIFT.

19:20.768 --> 19:22.552
I'VE GOTTA BE BACK
TO WORK IN AN HOUR.

19:22.683 --> 19:24.163
-BUT I CAME WITH TODD.

19:24.293 --> 19:25.729
-I DON'T CARE.

19:25.860 --> 19:27.427
-I DON'T MIND TAKING
HER HOME, MRS. MORGAN.

19:27.557 --> 19:29.298
-I TOLD YOU TO STOP SEEING
KIRSTIE AND I MEAN IT.

19:29.429 --> 19:30.778
-KIRSTIE: YOU CAN'T DO THIS.

19:30.908 --> 19:33.041
-YES, I CAN AND I WILL.
YOU'RE NOT 18 YET.

19:33.172 --> 19:34.956
AND I'LL CALL THE POLICE
AND HAVE YOU ARRESTED

19:35.086 --> 19:37.306
IF YOU DON'T STAY
AWAY FROM MY DAUGHTER.

19:37.437 --> 19:39.787
-I'LL KEEP SEEING TODD.
I SWEAR TO GOD, MOM.

19:39.917 --> 19:41.615
YOU CAN'T STOP ME. NOTHING CAN.

19:42.311 --> 19:44.226
-WELL, MAYBE A NEW
TOWN, A DIFFERENT SCHOOL

19:44.357 --> 19:45.923
MIGHT BE JUST WHAT
YOU NEED RIGHT NOW.

19:46.054 --> 19:47.229
LET'S GO.
-KIRSTIE: NO.

19:49.275 --> 19:50.319
-LET'S GO.

19:54.497 --> 19:57.413
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

19:57.544 --> 19:59.328
-TODD AND KIRSTIE
REALLY LOVE EACH OTHER.

19:59.459 --> 20:01.330
I MEAN, ONE LOOK
AND YOU CAN SEE IT,

20:01.461 --> 20:03.463
BUT THEIR PARENTS WON'T
LET THEM GET TOGETHER.

20:03.593 --> 20:05.029
-MANNY, THEIR
PARENTS ARE PROBABLY

20:05.160 --> 20:07.206
JUST TRYIN' TO DO WHAT'S
RIGHT FOR THEIR KIDS.

20:07.336 --> 20:08.946
-I KNOW.

20:09.077 --> 20:11.079
THEY'RE TRYIN' TO DO WHAT'S
RIGHT FOR THEMSELVES.

20:12.385 --> 20:14.125
HEY, THAT'S TODD'S CAR.

20:19.130 --> 20:22.003
"DEAR MANNY, WE WERE BOTH
PROUD TO CALL YOU FRIEND.

20:22.133 --> 20:25.224
THE CAR IS YOURS.
GOODBYE. TODD AND KIRSTIE."

20:25.354 --> 20:26.573
-LET ME SEE THAT.

20:28.575 --> 20:30.533
WHEN WAS THE LAST
TIME YOU SAW THEM?

20:31.273 --> 20:34.015
-AT THE HOUSE, IN THE DRIVEWAY.

20:34.145 --> 20:35.321
TODD WAS LEAVIN' TO GET KIRSTIE,

20:35.451 --> 20:37.236
SAID THEY WERE GONNA
GO TO PRACTICE.

20:39.412 --> 20:41.457
WAIT. OH, MAN.

20:41.979 --> 20:44.112
TODD SAID THEY WERE GONNA
GO TO THE DIVING BOARD,

20:44.243 --> 20:46.593
BUT I FIGURED THEY WERE GONNA
GO TO THE SWIMMING POOL.

20:46.723 --> 20:48.508
THERE'S THIS OTHER PLACE
THE LOCAL KIDS CALL THE--

20:48.638 --> 20:49.987
-DIVING BOARD,
PALOS VERDES CLIFFS.

20:50.118 --> 20:51.206
I KNOW THE PLACE. COME ON.

20:52.512 --> 20:54.340
-TODD, COULD WE JUST
GO SOMEWHERE?

20:54.470 --> 20:55.863
RUN AWAY?

20:56.733 --> 21:00.607
-NO. I KNOW THEY'D FIND US
AND BRING US BACK.

21:02.696 --> 21:04.611
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY, KIRSTIE.

21:07.440 --> 21:09.572
THIS IS THE ONLY WAY
FOR US TO BE TOGETHER.

21:13.489 --> 21:15.186
WHAT'D YOU WRITE?

21:18.407 --> 21:20.322
-"I DON'T WANT TO
LIVE WITHOUT TODD.

21:21.802 --> 21:23.456
"IF YOU WON'T LET US
BE TOGETHER HERE...

21:27.329 --> 21:29.288
WE'LL GO WHERE
YOU CAN'T STOP US."

21:29.810 --> 21:33.030
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

21:33.161 --> 21:34.380
WHAT DID YOU WRITE?

21:37.339 --> 21:39.559
-"I KNOW THAT I HAVE
TO BE WITH KIRSTIE,

21:41.648 --> 21:43.780
OR I HAVE NO REASON
TO BE AT ALL."

21:45.042 --> 21:47.349
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

21:59.622 --> 22:01.015
I LOVE YOU.

22:02.016 --> 22:05.454
-I LOVE YOU, TOO. FOREVER.

22:05.585 --> 22:07.238
-FOREVER.

22:10.546 --> 22:14.245
[SORROWFUL ORCHESTRAL MUSIC]

22:30.784 --> 22:34.483
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

22:52.414 --> 22:53.937
-NO!

22:55.199 --> 22:57.376
[WATER SPLASHES]

23:01.249 --> 23:02.903
[GASPING]

23:03.033 --> 23:07.211
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

23:13.217 --> 23:16.307
TODD, TODD, TODD.

23:16.438 --> 23:20.094
TODD. PLEASE DON'T DIE.

23:20.224 --> 23:24.011
[BOAT MOTOR HUMMING]

23:36.153 --> 23:37.503
-ALL RIGHT, I GOT HIM.
LET HIM GO.

23:37.633 --> 23:39.200
-NO, DON'T TAKE HIM!
-MITCH: LET HIM GO!

23:40.027 --> 23:41.898
-HE'S GOT HIM.
-KIRSTIE: TODD!

23:42.029 --> 23:43.378
-OKAY, HE'S GOT HIM.

23:44.901 --> 23:46.686
[GASPING]

23:46.816 --> 23:49.515
-TODD. TODD!

23:51.430 --> 23:52.561
TODD, NO!

23:52.692 --> 23:54.215
-LISTEN TO ME.
LISTEN TO ME.

23:54.345 --> 23:55.738
DO YOU WANT HIM TO LIVE, HUH?
[KIRSTIE CRYING]

23:55.869 --> 23:57.218
OKAY, THEN LET
THEM DO THEIR JOB.

23:59.481 --> 24:01.004
-NO PULSE. BEGIN CPR.

24:01.135 --> 24:02.092
-I'LL GET US OUTTA HERE.

24:03.790 --> 24:05.052
-MITCH: ONE, TWO, THREE--

24:05.182 --> 24:06.749
-BAYWATCH ONE
TO HEADQUARTERS.

24:06.880 --> 24:08.534
HAVE PARAMEDICS AND AMBULANCE
MEET US AT THE MARINA.

24:08.664 --> 24:10.884
NOTIFY SAINT JOHN'S. WE'RE
IN ROUTE WITH A FULL ARREST.

24:11.014 --> 24:12.973
-FOUR, FIVE.

24:13.103 --> 24:16.280
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.
[BOAT MOTORS REV]

24:16.411 --> 24:19.370
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.

24:19.501 --> 24:21.198
COME ON!

24:21.329 --> 24:23.897
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE.
-KIRSTIE: IS HE GONNA DIE?

24:24.027 --> 24:25.289
-NO.

24:27.204 --> 24:29.250
-IF HE DIES,
I WANNA DIE WITH HIM.

24:29.380 --> 24:31.078
I DON'T WANNA BE WITHOUT HIM.

24:31.208 --> 24:33.080
-LOOK, THIS ISN'T
ABOUT YOU DYING.

24:33.210 --> 24:35.212
IT'S ABOUT HIM LIVING.

24:36.257 --> 24:39.086
-ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR.

24:39.216 --> 24:42.219
-HOW CAN YOU DO THIS? HOW?

24:43.307 --> 24:45.092
[SIGHS]

24:45.222 --> 24:47.442
CAN YOU POSSIBLY IMAGINE HOW
I FELT WHEN THE POLICE CALLED?

24:48.356 --> 24:49.618
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

24:49.749 --> 24:51.098
-TO SEE TODD.
-MRS. ROSE: THAT'S HER.

24:51.228 --> 24:52.534
-KIRSTIE, COME BACK HERE!

24:52.665 --> 24:54.188
-SHE DID IT TO HIM,
THAT LITTLE TRAMP.

24:55.232 --> 24:57.191
-DON'T YOU CALL
MY DAUGHTER THAT!

24:57.321 --> 24:59.236
I TRIED TO KEEP YOUR
SPOILED LITTLE BRAT

24:59.367 --> 25:00.803
FROM SEEING KIRSTIE.

25:00.934 --> 25:03.284
HE ALMOST KILLED HER!
I'M FILING CHARGES.

25:03.414 --> 25:05.765
-ARE YOU TRYING TO GET
SOME MONEY OUT OF THIS?

25:05.895 --> 25:07.680
LISTEN,
MY ATTORNEY WILL EAT YOU

25:07.810 --> 25:09.029
AND YOUR DAUGHTER FOR LUNCH!

25:09.159 --> 25:10.073
-OUR SON HAD
NOTHING TO DO WITH--

25:10.204 --> 25:11.031
-KNOCK IT OFF!

25:11.597 --> 25:12.467
-WHO ARE YOU?

25:13.381 --> 25:14.774
-I'M THE LIFEGUARD THAT
PULLED YOUR CHILDREN

25:14.904 --> 25:16.079
OUT OF THE SURF TODAY.

25:17.254 --> 25:18.821
THEY TRIED TO KILL THEMSELVES.

25:24.044 --> 25:25.001
-SUICIDE?

25:28.048 --> 25:31.530
NO, NOT MY SON. NOT TODD.

25:31.660 --> 25:34.794
-THEY JUMPED OFF
THE CLIFF ON PURPOSE.

25:38.624 --> 25:40.713
-I DON'T KNOW WHAT
SHE WAS THINKING.

25:40.843 --> 25:42.018
-WELL, YOU BETTER FIND OUT.

25:43.237 --> 25:44.673
LOOK, YOU BETTER GET THESE
KIDS INTO COUNSELING,

25:44.804 --> 25:46.109
TALK TO 'EM.

25:46.240 --> 25:47.981
FIND OUT WHAT THEIR
LIVES ARE ABOUT.

25:48.721 --> 25:50.026
GIVE 'EM A CHANCE.

25:54.901 --> 25:59.558
[LIGHT PIANO MUSIC]

25:59.688 --> 26:02.691
[INDISTINCT TALKING
OVER SPEAKER]

26:05.955 --> 26:08.349
[MONITOR BEEPING]

26:08.479 --> 26:09.916
-HOW'S HE DOING?

26:13.484 --> 26:15.008
IT'S REALLY GOOD
THAT YOU'RE HERE.

26:17.924 --> 26:19.403
-DO YOU THINK
HE KNOWS I'M HERE?

26:24.670 --> 26:26.410
HE WAS ALWAYS SO GOOD TO ME.

26:28.238 --> 26:29.413
I NEVER DID ANYTHING RIGHT.

26:30.719 --> 26:32.808
I WAS HEAVY AND CLUMSY.

26:35.071 --> 26:36.638
HE TAUGHT ME HOW TO DIVE.

26:38.292 --> 26:39.989
HE'D TELL ME I WAS PRETTY.

26:41.512 --> 26:43.036
HE MADE ME FEEL PRETTY.

26:45.734 --> 26:47.780
[KIRSTIE CRYING]

26:47.910 --> 26:49.782
I'D BE SO AFRAID WITHOUT HIM.

26:52.523 --> 26:54.308
I'M SO AFRAID HE'LL HATE ME.

26:56.179 --> 26:57.920
-WHY? WHY WOULD BE HATE YOU?

27:00.619 --> 27:03.491
-I CHICKENED OUT.
I WENT INTO A TUCK.

27:05.275 --> 27:08.061
-NO. YOU DECIDED THAT
YOU WANTED TO LIVE.

27:08.191 --> 27:10.063
-BUT WE AGREED TO BE TOGETHER.

27:10.193 --> 27:11.412
WE MADE A PACT.

27:12.587 --> 27:14.850
-WELL, THERE'S NO
TOGETHERNESS IN DEATH.

27:14.981 --> 27:16.852
[KIRSTIE CRYING]

27:16.983 --> 27:19.550
I KNOW THERE'S NOTHING.

27:21.204 --> 27:23.293
THERE'S NO HOLDING
HANDS, THERE'S,

27:24.294 --> 27:26.253
THERE'S NO ROMANCE,
THERE'S NO LOVE.

27:26.383 --> 27:30.387
IT'S EMPTINESS. IT'S
EMPTINESS WHERE YOU USED TO BE.

27:34.391 --> 27:37.264
I THINK THAT IF
THERE IS A HEAVEN

27:37.394 --> 27:42.008
OR SOME SORT OF
AN AFTER LIFE, [SIGHS]

27:42.138 --> 27:44.445
WELL, I GUARANTEE YOU THAT
YOU WOULD NOT BE REWARDED

27:44.575 --> 27:45.925
FOR TRYIN' TO TAKE
YOUR OWN LIVES.

27:48.710 --> 27:50.886
[KIRSTIE SNIFFLES]

27:52.409 --> 27:56.196
KIRSTIE, NO MATTER
HOW BAD IT SEEMS...

27:57.414 --> 28:00.330
OR HOW MUCH IT HURTS,

28:01.331 --> 28:02.681
THERE'S ALWAYS HOPE.

28:03.899 --> 28:05.988
THERE IS AS LONG
AS YOU'RE ALIVE.

28:12.865 --> 28:14.475
-I WAS DOWN 300 FEET, C.J.

28:14.605 --> 28:15.955
I USED
A SLED AND THE BALLOON.

28:16.085 --> 28:17.521
-OH, YOU WON'T HAVE
TO DIVE THAT FAR.

28:17.652 --> 28:19.480
IF MELLISANDE'S DOWN
THERE, SHE'LL FIND YOU.

28:19.610 --> 28:20.655
SHE'LL SENSE YOU.

28:20.786 --> 28:22.657
-[SIGHS] ALL RIGHT.

28:26.443 --> 28:27.575
AREN'T YOU GONNA DIVE WITH ME?

28:27.706 --> 28:29.098
-NO, I'M GONNA
WAIT ON THE BOAT.

28:29.795 --> 28:31.666
IF SHE SENSES I'M WITH YOU,
SHE MIGHT NOT SHOW.

28:31.797 --> 28:33.450
-ALL RIGHT. YOU STAY
AND GUARD THE BOAT.

28:33.581 --> 28:35.148
I'LL GO TALK TO THE MERMAID.

28:37.411 --> 28:38.281
-GO AHEAD.

28:40.153 --> 28:41.328
-THIS IS GOOD.

28:41.458 --> 28:42.764
HERE I GO.

28:42.895 --> 28:44.418
[WATER SPLASHES]

28:46.768 --> 28:50.554
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

29:08.268 --> 29:11.010
[WATER BUBBLING]

29:15.449 --> 29:19.018
[DREAMY MUSIC]

29:20.236 --> 29:21.672
-CHRISTOPHER!

29:22.804 --> 29:24.588
-MY NAME IS CODY.

29:27.374 --> 29:31.508
[DREAMY MUSIC]

29:34.990 --> 29:36.905
-COME WITH ME, CHRISTOPHER.

29:38.864 --> 29:41.214
-I CAN'T.
I'M RUNNING OUT OF AIR.

29:43.912 --> 29:47.394
[DREAMY MUSIC]

29:49.352 --> 29:51.006
HOW CAN I STAY?

29:56.664 --> 29:58.535
NO, MELLISANDE, NO.

29:59.885 --> 30:03.366
-I HAVE WORN THIS A HUNDRED
YEARS, SINCE THE STORM.

30:04.019 --> 30:05.455
I HAVE WAITED FOR
YOU, CHRISTOPHER.

30:06.413 --> 30:07.414
DON'T YOU REMEMBER?

30:07.544 --> 30:09.068
YOU GAVE ME THIS.

30:12.332 --> 30:15.552
[SOULFUL HUMMING]

30:21.994 --> 30:25.040
WE PROMISED TO BE
TOGETHER, FOREVER.

30:25.649 --> 30:26.737
[WATER SPLASHES]

30:26.868 --> 30:30.567
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

30:35.181 --> 30:36.835
-CODY: MELLISANDE!

30:39.881 --> 30:42.579
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

30:49.543 --> 30:51.545
MELLISANDE, MELLISANDE!

30:55.679 --> 30:58.595
[WATER BUBBLING]

31:00.597 --> 31:02.773
[OXYGEN TANK RASPING]

31:03.687 --> 31:05.080
-COME ON, TELL ME.

31:05.211 --> 31:06.168
YOU WERE DOWN THERE FOR
EIGHT MINUTES, CODY.

31:06.299 --> 31:07.517
I KNOW SOMETHING HAPPENED.

31:07.648 --> 31:09.171
-MELLISANDE.
-C.J.: YOU SAW HER?

31:09.302 --> 31:10.781
-CODY: SHE GAVE ME AIR!

31:10.912 --> 31:12.305
-I KNEW SHE WAS REAL.

31:12.435 --> 31:14.176
-WE TALKED. I DON'T KNOW
EXACTLY HOW, BUT WE DID.

31:14.307 --> 31:15.482
-TELEPATHY!

31:15.612 --> 31:17.310
-YEAH.
SHE THINKS I'M SOMEONE,

31:17.440 --> 31:19.181
SOMEONE NAMED CHRISTOPHER.

31:19.312 --> 31:21.401
SOME SAILOR WHO'S SHIP SANK
IN A STORM A HUNDRED YEARS AGO.

31:22.489 --> 31:24.186
-OH, THAT'S SO ROMANTIC.

31:33.761 --> 31:37.808
[MYSTICAL MUSIC]

31:43.075 --> 31:45.860
-CHRISTOPHER, NO!

31:50.343 --> 31:51.605
[TODD COUGHING]

31:51.735 --> 31:52.606
-TODD!

31:53.520 --> 31:56.740
OH! THANK GOD
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT.

31:57.524 --> 31:58.786
-WHAT HAPPENED?

32:00.092 --> 32:04.270
-WHAT WE TRIED
TO DO, KILLING OURSELVES,

32:05.619 --> 32:06.663
WAS WRONG.

32:06.794 --> 32:07.926
IT WAS SO WRONG.

32:11.320 --> 32:13.192
-MY PARENTS. DO THEY--

32:13.322 --> 32:15.020
-THEY'RE DOWN THE
HALL WITH MY MOM.

32:16.369 --> 32:18.066
EVERYBODY'S YELLING
AT EACH OTHER.

32:20.460 --> 32:21.504
-I GOTTA GET OUT OF HERE.

32:21.635 --> 32:22.853
-NO, TODD. YOU'RE TOO WEAK!

32:25.030 --> 32:26.596
WHERE ARE WE GONNA GO?

32:26.727 --> 32:29.599
-SOMEPLACE. SOMEPLACE
WHERE WE CAN BE TOGETHER.

32:30.731 --> 32:32.863
-TODD, I DON'T WANT TO.

32:34.213 --> 32:35.344
-NOT THAT.

32:37.825 --> 32:39.087
MEXICO.

32:39.218 --> 32:42.177
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

32:45.659 --> 32:46.921
-WE'VE GOTTA FIND THEM FAST.

32:47.052 --> 32:49.097
HE COULD SUFFER
SECONDARY DROWNING.

32:49.228 --> 32:50.620
-WHAT'S THAT?

32:50.751 --> 32:51.882
-WHEN SOMEBODY ALMOST
DROWNS, LIKE TODD,

32:52.013 --> 32:53.275
THEY INHALE SALT WATER.

32:53.406 --> 32:55.060
-BUT HE WOKE UP, HE'S OKAY.

32:55.190 --> 32:56.800
-I KNOW, I KNOW, BUT THE
SALT IS STILL IN HIS LUNGS.

32:56.931 --> 32:59.064
-SO THE BODY MANUFACTURES
FLUID TO DILUTE THE SALT.

32:59.847 --> 33:01.283
-SO WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

33:01.414 --> 33:03.198
-I'M SAYING THAT IF WE
DON'T FIND TODD QUICKLY,

33:03.329 --> 33:04.678
HE COULD DROWN INTERNALLY.

33:04.808 --> 33:07.724
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

33:11.598 --> 33:14.470
-WE'VE GOTTA GO BACK.
I'M SCARED, TODD.

33:14.601 --> 33:17.125
[TODD COUGHS]

33:19.432 --> 33:21.042
TODD, I'M SCARED.

33:22.870 --> 33:24.654
YOUR COUGH IS GETTING WORSE.

33:24.785 --> 33:26.482
-[GASPING] I'M OKAY.

33:29.007 --> 33:32.836
-TODD, PLEASE.
I DON'T WANT YOU TO DIE.

33:33.707 --> 33:35.143
I DON'T WANNA DIE.

33:35.752 --> 33:37.102
NOT NOW.

33:37.232 --> 33:38.451
-[COUGHS] I'M GONNA SHOW THEM

33:38.581 --> 33:40.235
THAT THEY CAN'T CONTROL MY LIFE.

33:40.366 --> 33:43.499
[TODD GASPING]

33:43.630 --> 33:46.241
-YOU'RE USING THIS TO GET EVEN
WITH YOUR PARENTS.

33:46.372 --> 33:49.636
-NO. [COUGHS]

33:55.424 --> 33:56.382
-THE HARBOR MASTER
SAYS HE SAW THEM

33:56.512 --> 33:57.905
ABOUT HALF AN HOUR AGO.

33:58.036 --> 33:59.863
-MAYBE THEY'RE JUST
HIDING ON THE BOAT.

33:59.994 --> 34:01.778
-OKAY, THEY SAID SLIP 27.

34:04.694 --> 34:05.565
OH. THEY'RE GONE.

34:06.174 --> 34:07.262
-WHERE COULD THEY HAVE GONE?

34:07.393 --> 34:08.784
-I DON'T KNOW, ANYWHERE.

34:08.916 --> 34:10.309
DOESN'T MATTER WHEN
YOU'RE RUNNING AWAY.

34:10.438 --> 34:12.353
COME ON, WE BETTER GET
THE COASTIES IN ON THIS.

34:13.920 --> 34:17.141
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

34:19.882 --> 34:21.233
[TODD GASPING]

34:21.362 --> 34:23.670
-TODD, PLEASE. LET'S GO BACK.

34:23.800 --> 34:26.194
-[GASPING] I WON'T.

34:29.676 --> 34:31.330
-TODD!

34:32.547 --> 34:35.246
TODD! TODD!

34:36.291 --> 34:38.902
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

34:44.168 --> 34:45.431
HELP!

34:46.301 --> 34:49.174
PLEASE! CAN ANYBODY HEAR ME?

34:50.827 --> 34:53.178
PLEASE, HELP!
SOMEBODY, PLEASE!

34:53.308 --> 34:55.397
CAN ANYBODY HEAR ME?

34:59.619 --> 35:02.839
[BOAT MOTOR HUMMING]

35:05.190 --> 35:07.627
-BAYWATCH ONE TO COAST
GUARD AIR, DO YOU READ?

35:07.757 --> 35:09.368
-MAN ON RADIO:
ROGER, BAYWATCH ONE.

35:09.498 --> 35:11.805
-THE BOAT'S ABOUT
ONE HALF MILE FROM US.

35:11.935 --> 35:13.502
-MAN ON RADIO: BAYWATCH
ONE, RESCUE 6503,

35:13.633 --> 35:15.765
I'M AT YOUR SIX,
ONE QUARTER MILE OUT.

35:15.896 --> 35:17.027
-DONNA: SHE SAID
HE WAS UNCONSCIOUS

35:17.158 --> 35:18.768
AND HAVING TROUBLE BREATHING.

35:18.899 --> 35:20.118
WE'LL HELP WITH THE HOIST
ONCE WE'RE ON THE SCENE.

35:20.988 --> 35:22.859
-ROGER, BAYWATCH ONE.

35:24.165 --> 35:27.821
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:30.998 --> 35:33.957
[BOAT MOTOR HUMMING]

35:37.265 --> 35:39.659
-HERE, OVER HERE!
HURRY, PLEASE!

35:39.789 --> 35:43.793
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:48.885 --> 35:51.236
HE'S UP HERE.
HELP HIM, PLEASE.

35:52.193 --> 35:54.717
HE CAN'T BREATHE.
PLEASE HELP HIM.

35:55.979 --> 35:57.894
-MANNY, HELP WITH
THE RESCUE VEST.

36:00.375 --> 36:01.898
HIS LUNGS
ARE FILLED WITH FLUID.

36:05.163 --> 36:08.992
[HELICOPTER WHIRRING]

36:25.661 --> 36:26.880
-MAN: BASKET AWAY.

36:29.622 --> 36:32.407
[HELICOPTER WHIRRING]

36:34.714 --> 36:36.106
-SURE YOU WANNA DO THIS?

36:36.237 --> 36:37.369
-ABSOLUTELY.

36:38.631 --> 36:41.634
-ALL RIGHT. WELL, IF YOU SEE
HER, WHAT ARE YOU GONNA SAY?

36:42.243 --> 36:44.854
-THAT YOU'RE NOT HER
CHRISTOPHER. YOU'RE MY CODY.

36:46.813 --> 36:48.641
[WATER SPLASHES]

36:48.771 --> 36:52.427
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC]

36:57.998 --> 37:01.610
[OXYGEN RESPIRATOR RASPING]

37:09.966 --> 37:11.794
[C.J. GRUNTS]

37:14.406 --> 37:17.670
[WATER BUBBLING]

37:19.324 --> 37:21.326
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

37:26.200 --> 37:29.247
[MYSTICAL MUSIC]

37:33.903 --> 37:37.559
[OMINOUS MUSIC]

37:52.879 --> 37:56.274
-NEVER LOSE
YOUR LOVE. GOODBYE.

38:01.844 --> 38:05.718
[MYSTICAL MUSIC]

38:11.027 --> 38:12.986
-WHAT HAPPENED?
-C.J.: I'M NOT QUITE SURE.

38:13.116 --> 38:14.117
-ARE YOU OKAY?

38:14.248 --> 38:15.467
-YEAH.

38:17.556 --> 38:18.426
-WELL...

38:20.385 --> 38:22.125
-BUT WAIT A SECOND,
THIS ISN'T MINE.

38:25.607 --> 38:27.740
OH, MY GOD, CODY.
THAT LOOKS JUST LIKE YOU.

38:28.915 --> 38:30.308
-THIS MUST BE CHRISTOPHER.

38:30.438 --> 38:32.005
-OH.

38:32.135 --> 38:33.441
-NOW WE CAN FINALLY PROVE
THAT WE'RE NOT CRAZY.

